### Configuration

~~~ .php
File::$state = [
    // Range of allowed file sizes
    'size' => [ … ],
    // List of allowed file types
    'type' => [ … ],
    // List of allowed file extensions
    'x' => [ … ]
];
~~~

Create an empty file or open file if it already exists:

~~~ .php
$file = new File('.\path\to\file.txt');
~~~
